{
  "texts": [
    "In these instances, I encourage my students to utilise ChatGPT as a resource to simplify complex English language questions and to obtain specific stepby-step guidance.",
    "It is a valuable aid in enhancing their understanding and enabling them to execute tasks more efficiently (P2).",
    "Two participants further referred to translation and how they used or would like to use ChatGPT.",
    "One indicated that they would prefer to use ChatGPT for translation but that \"ChatGPT is not capable of translating content from English to IsiZulu\".",
    "IsiZulu is one of the twelve official languages in South Africa."
  ]
}